name: Basic Shapes Candle - Black
description:
The Basic Shapes special edition, limited and numbered to 300 copies, double wall fine faience cup designed by Jorge Trindade and João Seco. This cup was originally designed for Musa in 2005.
Fine faience cups and packaging were produced with local raw materials and manufactured in Portugal, by skilled artisans, in compliance with all the guidelines to safeguard the environment.


Technical details:
Double-wall cup in white faiance
Cup size approx. Exterior: ø 85mm x 115mm (Height)
Box size: 100mm (W) x 100mm (D) x 120mm (Height)

<u>Black Vanilla fragrance</u>

name: Nothing Lasts Forever Magazine Vol.1 to 8 ** Last Copies **
description: Compilation book with 8 online issues of international project NLF Magazine, featuring artists from all over the world. Artists: I am always hungry, Dialéctica, Teis Albers Phoenixart, Radiographics, Gluekit Graphicscenery, Volk, Picnic Industries, Humanempire, Rangerbastards, Ilike drawing, Perfornika, Laikabase, Jeremy Ville, Just another reason, Robonut, Hellovon and others… Published by Basheer Graphic Books Singapore Edited by MusaCollective, Portugal 288 pages 16,2 x 22,5 cm More info: www.basheergraphic.com www.nlfmagazine.com
